window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Hollywood has always been a cutthroat industry, but for Sophie Paulson, the backstabbing turns personal when her movie producer boyfriend, Paul Franklin, dumps her for another woman, then fires her out of the blue. Former actress turned amateur sleuth Hope Hadley arrives in town just as Paul is found murdered and the police suspect Sophie of the crime. Hope desperately races to discover the truth before her friend Sophie is put in jail for the rest of her life.</p> <p>Titles in The Hope Hadley series:</p> <p></p> <ol> <li><i>Fame Is a Killer</i></li> <li><i>Fishing for a Murderer</i></li> <li><i>Murder of a Yoga Instructor</i></li> <li><i>Drowning in Deceit</i></li> <li><i>A Not So Merry Christmas Murder</i></li> <li><i>Killer Injustice</i></li> <li><i>Murder of a Restaurant Critic</i></li> <li><i>Murder of a Movie Producer</i></li> <li><i>The Killer Holiday Office Party</i></li> </ol> <p>All of the Hope Hadley books can be listened to in any order.</p>"; 
